//
// Renders "type 4" Cairo pentagonal tilings. See
// https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cairo_pentagonal_tiling
// for details.
//
// Inspired by https://twitter.com/cs_kaplan
//
// Related shaders:
//
//   - "Cairo tiling" by nimitz
//      https://www.shadertoy.com/view/4ssSWf
